---
---

<section class="mt-10 mb-14">
  <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-elevated shadow-sm overflow-hidden font-mono text-sm">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 px-4 py-2.5 border-b border-border bg-bg">
      <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-400"></span>
      <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400"></span>
      <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-400"></span>
      <span class="ml-2 text-xs text-text-secondary">user@blog — zsh</span>
    </div>
    <div class="p-5 space-y-3">
      <div class="typing-line">
        <span class="text-accent">➜</span> <span class="text-text-secondary">~</span> <span class="text-text">whoami</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pl-4 text-text-secondary output-line">
        一位熱愛技術與寫作的開發者。這裡是思考與紀錄的空間。
      </div>
      <div class="typing-line">
        <span class="text-accent">➜</span> <span class="text-text-secondary">~</span> <span class="text-text">cat motto.txt</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pl-4 text-text-secondary output-line">
        好的技術文章不只傳遞知識，也傳遞觀點。
      </div>
      <div class="typing-line">
        <span class="text-accent">➜</span> <span class="text-text-secondary">~</span> <span class="animate-pulse">▌</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .typing-line {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease forwards;
  }
  .output-line {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease forwards;
  }
  .typing-line:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .output-line:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
  .typing-line:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1.4s; }
  .output-line:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 2.0s; }
  .typing-line:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 2.6s; }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(4px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
</style>
